                | This was a project carried out in the first cycle as a student of the degree
                | Software design and development.
              a.portfolio__link(href='https://github.com/DanniDevv/best-movie')
                | See Work 
                i.bi.bi-arrow-right
          .portfolio__box
            .portfolio__img
              img(src='assets/smartparking.png', alt='Portfolio Items')
            .portfolio__info
              h3.portfolio__title Smart Parking
              p.portfolio__content
                | This was a project created together in order to improve
                | the shape of the parking lots.
              a.portfolio__link(href='https://github.com/DanniDevv/api-SmartParking')
                | See Work 
                i.bi.bi-arrow-right
